#  ... loop continues ...
#
# Reading: the FIRST failure (09:02:12) is the cause — a bad DB password, NOT a
# code crash. Every restart after is the LOOP, repeating the same root failure.
# Reading only the latest "Started ..." line would mislead you into thinking it
# is recovering. Fix the credential; the loop stops.
